autocmd BufReadPost * if line("'\"") > 1 && line("'\"") <= line("$") | exe "normal! g'\"" | endif
autocmd FocusGained,BufEnter * silent! checktime
autocmd VimLeave * mksession! $HOME/.config/vim/session.vim
colorscheme desert
filetype indent on
filetype plugin on
syntax on

